<p class="indent4" style="-uslm-lc:I16" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Subclause (II) shall not apply to any indebtedness incurred on or before <date date="2017-12-15">December 15, 2017</date>, and, in applying such subclause to any indebtedness incurred after such date, the limitation under such subclause shall be reduced (but not below zero) by the amount of any indebtedness incurred on or before <date date="2017-12-15">December 15, 2017</date>, which is treated as acquisition indebtedness for purposes of this subsection for the taxable year.</p>
